          View Source Code
        </a>
        <a href="https://x.com/rustokwallet" target="_blank" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 28px;background:var(--surface);color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;">Follow Updates</a>
